The solution I use in PHP is the following:

&lt;FilesMatch &quot;^test$&quot;&gt;
    ForceType application/x-httpd-php
&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;

Then, I make sure to have a PHP file called &#39;test&#39; in the htdocs.  This is
the handler.  You can get everthing below it from the PATH_INFO CGI
variable.  I do no know what the appropriate Type would be for perl, but I&#39;m
sure it&#39;s easily found (if you don&#39;t already know it).

